view.assignments_categories

Class AssignmentTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.assignments_categories.AssignmentTree

  • public class AssignmentTree
extends java.lang.Object
    Category tree builds a hierarchical representation of categories and assignments. Each category is displayed with there children categories. Each category displays the percentage weight of their parent categories. This class also contains a maps that map a category name to the actual category.

    jamesfazio
